Introduction

All-Star is a male duo that is managed independently. The members are Noah and Joonhyeon. All-star was originally a five-member group who debuted with the song "Sugar" on August 1st, 2015. After the departure of three members, All-Star continued to promote as a duo until they disbanded in 2017.
